{"word":"H7523 - רָצַח - râtsach - raw-tsakh' - Put to death","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָצַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râtsach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-tsakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Put to death"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொன்றுபோடு, ஜீவனை வாங்கு, கொலைசெய், கொன்றவள், கொலைபாதகன், கொலைசெய்தவனாயிரு, இரத்தப்பழி வாங்குறவனாயிரு, சங்கரிக்கப்படு, கொலைசெய்யப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to murder, to slay, to kill"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to murder, to slay"},{"paragraph":"1) premeditated"},{"paragraph":"2) accidental"},{"paragraph":"3) as avenger"},{"paragraph":"4) slayer (intentional) (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be slain"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to murder, to assassinate"},{"paragraph":"2) murderer, assassin (participle) (substantive)"},{"paragraph":"d) (Pual) to be killed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>dash</i> in pieces, that is, <i>kill</i> (a human being), especially to <i>murder: - </i>put to death, kill, (man-) slay (-er), murder (-er)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7523 - רָצַח - râtsach - raw-tsakh'/7523\">H7523</a>, <a href=\"#/H7524 - רֶצַח - retsach - reh-tsakh/7524\">H7524</a>, <a href=\"#/H7525 - רִצְיָא - Ritsyâʼ - rits-yaw'/7525\">H7525</a>, <a href=\"#/H7526 - רְצִין - Rᵉtsîyn - rets-een'/7526\">H7526</a>"}]}